76370c8b218eacfdf6a33bd4c311575a

is the md5 of the flag (remember the format of the flag: stuyctf{XXX_XXXXXXXXXXX_XXXXX}). It is consisted of a number between 0 and 1000, an underscore, a borough of New York City, another underscore, and a number between 10000 and 15000.
